    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《ASCENDANT》，在这里，你和你那支不太可能的英雄队伍，以及三颗生物核心，上演一场生死存亡的好戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/4bfc3b428bd01e5cbebba602780d6cb6.avif?t=1771926355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/6914e868e7dd2d9412307ca6b84f2cc2.poster.avif?t=1771926355\" width=612 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/6914e868e7dd2d9412307ca6b84f2cc2.webm?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/6914e868e7dd2d9412307ca6b84f2cc2.mp4?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《ASCENDANT》是强化版夺旗战。经过千年的冷冻沉眠，你醒来后发现世界已经彻底崩坏：变异生物横行、失控科技肆虐，而各方小队正在为装满琥珀的生物核心展开激战，这些生物核心关乎你的“暗影”生存。然而，这不仅仅是争夺战。每局游戏都独一无二。虚拟游戏导演会动态调整生物核心的位置、开放区域和突发事件，迫使你时刻适应，或者迎接死亡。四支队伍，三个生物核心……自己算算吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/884079b9ff7649aefba0b76aa6a74d16.avif?t=1771926355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/986285855e05f3f9a0580465164afc10.poster.avif?t=1771926355\" width=612 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/986285855e05f3f9a0580465164afc10.webm?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/986285855e05f3f9a0580465164afc10.mp4?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个决定都至关重要。能量要慎用——你们队伍的能量池会随着击败变异生物而增长，如何利用这点将决定胜负。在战斗中解锁武器和装备，抢占优势。无论是升级武器、布置陷阱，还是直接全力突袭，制胜的关键只有一个——快速适应，因为地图会摧毁你所有精心策划的战术。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/409e099e304004b91d1bbc7b51196735.avif?t=1771926355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/8c4c7485740ad1fd6859174d23d199c6.poster.avif?t=1771926355\" width=612 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/8c4c7485740ad1fd6859174d23d199c6.webm?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/8c4c7485740ad1fd6859174d23d199c6.mp4?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有哪两场游戏是一模一样的。从突袭空袭到突变巨兽，各种动态事件可能随时颠覆战局，粉碎任何精心制定的战略。致命生物和环境危机无处不在，风险飙升，混乱升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/491b6a506be365eb3950ecadb0555173.avif?t=1771926355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/34db096cc8d31355ac5320dde0571279.poster.avif?t=1771926355\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/34db096cc8d31355ac5320dde0571279.webm?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/34db096cc8d31355ac5320dde0571279.mp4?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微调角色的技能和特性，以适应你的游戏风格，无论你是终极生物核心窃贼还是队伍中的混乱万能牌角色。在两局游戏间隙，可以进入社交大厅，与竞争者决斗，或准备好迎接更多混乱。或者，如果你渴望更多的杀戮，可以进入雷霆竞技场——一个 PVP 竞技场，唯一的目标是活着（并且炫耀地）离开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场残酷的游戏。它是 BioPunk 风格。它是生存游戏，不会给你任何帮助……但它有史诗般的原声带（《最终倒计时》怎么样？）。《ASCENDANT》让行动充满不可预测性，风险高得让你血压飙升。带上你的智慧、最强的队伍，或许再带上一份遗嘱。你将需要这三样东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《ASCENDANT》，在这里，你和你那支不太可能的英雄队伍，以及三颗生物核心，上演一场生死存亡的好戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/badd20035d0e5c2b778a628d9bc6954c.avif?t=1771926355\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/f9154ba15528317d32ecb3869fba973e.poster.avif?t=1771926355\" width=612 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/f9154ba15528317d32ecb3869fba973e.webm?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803110/extras/f9154ba15528317d32ecb3869fba973e.mp4?t=1771926355\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >微调角色的技能和特性，以适应你的游戏风格，无论你是终极生物核心窃贼还是队伍中的混乱万能牌角色。在两局游戏间隙，可以进入社交大厅，与竞争者决斗，或准备好迎接更多混乱。或者，如果你渴望更多的杀戮，可以进入雷霆竞技场——一个 PVP 竞技场，唯一的目标是活着（并且炫耀地）离开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场残酷的游戏。它是 BioPunk 风格。它是生存游戏，不会给你任何帮助……但它有史诗般的原声带（《最终倒计时》怎么样？）。《ASCENDANT》让行动充满不可预测性，风险高得让你血压飙升。带上你的智慧、最强的队伍，或许再带上一份遗嘱。你将需要这三样东西。</p>",
